Description:
Some Fixes for Mint-X-gtk2-theme (by me). This is themes based on Mint-X from LinuxMint Releases.
Included gtk3 w/o diff. Only edited gtk2-theme.

Start (Based) on:
- mint-themes_1.2.8
- mint-themes_1.3.5
- mint-themes-gtk3_3.8-9
- mint-themes-gtk3_3.10-5
- mint-themes-gtk3_3.18+7

Sources, original gtk-theme(s):
2 -> http://packages.linuxmint.com/pool/main/m/mint-themes/
3 -> http://packages.linuxmint.com/pool/main/m/mint-themes-gtk3/


Changelog:

16 -> 16PF
[*] Gtk-Tabs
[*] Thunar-bookmarks HV-separator
[*] Font from GUI-settings
[*] Menu Panel - Icons, File - Edit - ...
[*] Scrollbar - trough-border - slider_width - stepper-size
[*] XFCE panel - Panel buttons - Color
[*] Bar-player - Qt4 / GTK+ (example Clementine: Analise/Vol/PBar)

17 -> 17QF
[*] bar-player
[*] XFCE panel - Start/Up\Down - Size-button-xfce4panel
[*] Gtk-Tabs
[*] Bottom-File-buttons
[*] Scroll
[*] Thunar - Bookmarks|FM
[*] window-dragging

17QF2-16GTK3
[+] This theme using for gtk2 - 17QF and gtk3 from linuxmint-16

17QF2-18GTK3
[+] gtk3 from linuxmint-18 and gtk2 - 17QF

